data.description: Super cute home have so much to offer. 4 bed 2 bath in a cult sac and quiet neighborhood. In walking distance to schools, parks, and a grocery store.  Inside features open, split floor plan, high vaulted ceilings, spacious dining room, kitchen, gas stove, walk-in pantry, raised bar and good size living Room. LVP throughout the whole house. Tons of storage all over the home. Big laundry room over sized garage. Solar panels on home. Water softener and R/O System. Also has a camera system. Front has a patio area. Outback has tons of concrete. One size of the home features a HUGE RV pad with a full RV hook up. Other side of the home features another area to store more toys or plant a garden. Plenty of room for just about anything.
